  "texts": [
    "Needs of Appropriate Prompts.",
    "Among the tweets discussing the use of Chat-GPT to learn, \"prompts\" is frequently mentioned.",
    "They emphasized the importance of using appropriate prompts to maximize ChatGPT's effectiveness.",
    "Many users who had experiences asking ChatGPT with various tasks refined and shared prompts on Twitter to benefit others, \"Getting crap results from ChatGPT?",
    "Give it a chance to learn, and feed it with tons of information."
